To keep from being
blown away by the
wind, they gather in clusters. They
do enjoy gentle
breezes, though.

Its body is so

It can be carried
away on even the
gentlest breeze. It may even float
all the way to the
next town.

being blown away.

Ce Pokmon flotte  la drive, port par le vent. Sil sent

autres Granivol pour ne pas tre emport par la bourrasque.
